                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6754" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1058</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9726 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石以砥焉，化钝为利——中兴通讯的股权激励之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Aiming at the goal, turning dullness into profit - ZTE&#39;s equity incentive road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冷昕，郑颖业，张君怡，吴莹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中兴通讯股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权激励；激励动因；激励方案；实施效果</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Equity incentive; Incentive motivation; Incentive scheme; Implementation effect</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着经济全球化进程的不断加深以及中国经济体制的持续完善，越来越多的公司选择实施股权激励。股权激励作为一种长期激励工具，利用附加条件给予员工部分股东权益，促进股东与经理层的目标及利益趋于一致，增强了员工主人翁意识，从而起到实现人才战略和提升企业绩效的作用。然而，不少公司的股权激励计划依然存在着方案设计不科学、实施效果不明显等诸多问题。中兴通讯作为较早的制定和实施股权激励的国企上市公司，具有一定的行业代表性。本案例重点描述了中兴通讯的发展历程及企业现状，梳理了中兴通讯从2007年至2022年里分别在2007年、2013年、2017年和2020年实施的四次股权激励计划的背景、方案内容及实际解锁情况，探究其方案设计的动态过程。本案例旨在培养学生探索股权激励的方案设计的目的与合理性，进而根据方案的实施效果进行综合分析评价的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the deepening of economic globalization and the continuous improvement of China&#39;s economic system, more and more companies choose to implement equity incentives. Equity incentives are a tool for long-term incentives. It uses conditionalities to grant the rights and interests of some shareholders to employees, and promotes the convergence of goals and interests of shareholders and managers. It enhances the sense of employee ownership, thus playing a role in achieving talent strategy and improving enterprise performance. However, there are still many problems in the equity incentive plans of many companies, such as unscientific scheme design and unclear implementation results. ZTE, as an early state-owned enterprise listed company to formulate and implement equity incentives, has a certain industry representation.This case describes the development process of ZTE and the current situation of the enterprise, and sorts out the background, content and actual unlocking of the four equity incentive plans implemented by ZTE from 2007 to 2022 in 2007, 2013, 2017 and 2020 respectively. The dynamic process of scheme design is explored. This case aims to cultivate the purpose and rationality of students to explore the design of equity incentives, and to cultivate students&#39; ability to comprehensively analyse and evaluate according to the implementation effect of the program.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《高级财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权激励原理；SWOT分析法；期望理论；实施股权激励的优势；实施股权激励的弊端</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
